All Classes

Class Summary
Class
Description
Billet
This is the class to create the initial billet that will be machined in order to create the part
BilletDB
Contains CRUD methods to manage billet information kept in the database.
CarouselDB
Contains CRUD methods to manage carousel data in the database
CuttingTool
Holds all information related to a cutting tool and contains methods related
to cutting tool management and manipulation
CuttingToolDB
Contains CRUD methods to manage cutting tools in the database
CuttingToolProfile
Holds parameter values for the surface profile of the cutting tool.
CuttingToolProfileDB
Contains CRUD methods to manage cutting tool profiles files in the database
DB
Basic class for connecting and initialising the database.
KPIs
Holds values for virtual process KPIs and temporary stores simulation run
information that is required to do the simulation and report results.
LearningSet
Holds the parameter values for the trained model.
LearningSetDB
Contains CRUD methods to manage machine learning models in the database
Material
Holds the parameter values for billet materials.
MaterialDB
Contains CRUD methods to manage materials in the database
Nc
Holds the parameter values for NC files and the generated analysis files or reports.
NcDB
Contains CRUD methods to manage NC files in the database
SettingsDB
Utility class to retrieve or update the settings of the application
Add or remove a setting is not allowed as everything is created during database creation
SettingsSingleton
Holds the application global settings and is also used to store objects available
to multiple parallel threads.
SimulatorConfig
Contains simulator configuration parameters and corresponding getter
and setter methods.
